thread.title: Archie
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Archie

author: Archie
title: Archie
text: Booked through third party website. Service was good. Picked us on time at airport, drove to their office, car was ready, minimal form filling. Could have done with a bit more friendly service instead of the cold and unsmiling one we got. But rest all good. Again prompt attention while returning the car. Only took minutes and they took us back to the airport.
